<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Choose your announcement</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">
  We've prepared 4 realistic council announcements covering different priorities and use cases.
  Pick the one most relevant to your council's needs:
</p>

<div class="ndx-announcements-list">
  {% for announcement in sampleAnnouncements %}
    <div class="ndx-announcement-item">
      <h4 class="govuk-heading-s">
        {{ loop.index }}. {{ announcement.title }}
        <span class="govuk-tag" style="margin-left: 10px;">{{ announcement.category }}</span>
      </h4>

      <div class="govuk-grid-row">
        <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
          <div class="ndx-announcement-text">
            <p class="govuk-body-s" style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
              <strong>Full text:</strong>
            </p>
            <p class="govuk-body-s" style="font-style: italic; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 15px; border: 1px solid #b1b4b6;">
              {{ announcement.text }}
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="govuk-grid-column-one-third">
          <dl class="govuk-summary-list govuk-summary-list--no-border">
            <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
              <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">Length</dt>
              <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">{{ announcement.characterCount }} chars</dd>
            </div>
            <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
              <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">Cost</dt>
              <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">{{ announcement.estimatedCost }}</dd>
            </div>
            <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
              <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">Duration</dt>
              <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">{{ announcement.estimatedDuration }}</dd>
            </div>
          </dl>

          <div class="govuk-inset-text govuk-!-margin-top-3" style="padding: 10px;">
            <p class="govuk-body-s" style="margin-bottom: 5px;"><strong>Use case:</strong></p>
            <p class="govuk-body-s" style="margin-bottom: 0;">{{ announcement.useCase }}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="govuk-!-margin-top-3">
        <button type="button" class="govuk-button govuk-button--secondary" data-announcement-id="{{ announcement.id }}" onclick="copyAnnouncementText('{{ announcement.id }}', this)">
          Copy text to clipboard
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  {% endfor %}
</div>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m govuk-!-margin-top-6">Paste into Polly</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">
  After copying your chosen announcement:
</p>

<ol class="govuk-list govuk-list--number govuk-list--spaced">
  <li>
    <strong>Return to the Polly console tab</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Switch back to the browser tab with Amazon Polly open (from Step 1)
    </p>
  </li>

  <li>
    <strong>Clear the text input area</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Delete any test text from Step 1 so the input area is empty
    </p>
  </li>

  <li>
    <strong>Paste the announcement text</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Use Ctrl+V (Windows) or Cmd+V (Mac) to paste. The announcement should appear in the text box.
    </p>
  </li>

  <li>
    <strong>Verify character count</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Below the text input, you should see "X characters" matching the expected count for your
      chosen announcement (e.g., 427 characters for bin collection changes).
    </p>
  </li>
</ol>

<div class="govuk-inset-text">
  <p class="govuk-body">
    <strong>Why character count matters:</strong> Amazon Polly charges £0.016 per 1000 characters
    for neural voices. A 500-character announcement costs £0.008 (less than 1 penny). Knowing the
    character count helps you estimate costs for your council's announcements.
  </p>
</div>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Understanding announcement categories</h3>

<div class="ndx-category-guide">
  <h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Service Disruption (e.g., Bin Collection Changes)</h4>
  <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet govuk-body-s">
    <li><strong>Frequency:</strong> Weekly or bi-weekly</li>
    <li><strong>Urgency:</strong> Standard (24-48 hours notice)</li>
    <li><strong>Best voice:</strong> Amy (conversational, friendly)</li>
    <li><strong>Typical length:</strong> 300-500 characters</li>
    <li><strong>Delivery channels:</strong> Website, email alerts, phone hotline</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="ndx-category-guide govuk-!-margin-top-3">
  <h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Emergency Alert (e.g., Weather Warning)</h4>
  <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet govuk-body-s">
    <li><strong>Frequency:</strong> Rare (a few times per year)</li>
    <li><strong>Urgency:</strong> Urgent (immediate action required)</li>
    <li><strong>Best voice:</strong> Brian (authoritative, clear)</li>
    <li><strong>Typical length:</strong> 400-600 characters</li>
    <li><strong>Delivery channels:</strong> Website banner, phone hotline, social media, SMS</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="ndx-category-guide govuk-!-margin-top-3">
  <h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Committee Announcement (e.g., Planning Meeting)</h4>
  <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet govuk-body-s">
    <li><strong>Frequency:</strong> Monthly</li>
    <li><strong>Urgency:</strong> Standard (7-14 days notice)</li>
    <li><strong>Best voice:</strong> Emma (formal, professional)</li>
    <li><strong>Typical length:</strong> 500-700 characters</li>
    <li><strong>Delivery channels:</strong> Website, legal notices, email to stakeholders</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="ndx-category-guide govuk-!-margin-top-3">
  <h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Public Health (e.g., Vaccination Clinics)</h4>
  <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet govuk-body-s">
    <li><strong>Frequency:</strong> Seasonal or campaign-based</li>
    <li><strong>Urgency:</strong> Standard (ongoing information)</li>
    <li><strong>Best voice:</strong> Amy or Emma (reassuring, informative)</li>
    <li><strong>Typical length:</strong> 400-600 characters</li>
    <li><strong>Delivery channels:</strong> Website, community centers, phone hotline, posters</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m govuk-!-margin-top-6">Think about your council</h3>

<div class="ndx-reflection-box">
  <p class="govuk-body">
    <strong>Reflection prompt:</strong> Which type of announcement does your council publish most frequently?
  </p>
  <p class="govuk-body">
    Consider whether you publish more:
  </p>
  <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
    <li>Routine service updates (bin collections, road closures, library hours)</li>
    <li>Emergency alerts (weather, public safety, service outages)</li>
    <li>Formal committee notices (planning, licensing, consultations)</li>
    <li>Public health information (vaccinations, health campaigns, environmental health)</li>
  </ul>
  <p class="govuk-body">
    Understanding your mix helps estimate ROI - if you publish 50 service updates and 10 emergency
    alerts per year, text-to-speech saves 60 × £200 = £12,000 annually vs studio recording.
  </p>
</div>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Troubleshooting</h3>

<details class="govuk-details">
  <summary class="govuk-details__summary">
    <span class="govuk-details__summary-text">
      Copy to clipboard button not working
    </span>
  </summary>
  <div class="govuk-details__text">
    <p class="govuk-body">
      If the copy button doesn't work:
    </p>
    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
      <li>Manually select the announcement text (click and drag to highlight)</li>
      <li>Use Ctrl+C (Windows) or Cmd+C (Mac) to copy</li>
      <li>Check browser allows clipboard access (some browsers block this for security)</li>
      <li>Try a different browser (Chrome, Firefox, Safari all support clipboard API)</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</details>

<details class="govuk-details">
  <summary class="govuk-details__summary">
    <span class="govuk-details__summary-text">
      Character count in Polly doesn't match expected
    </span>
  </summary>
  <div class="govuk-details__text">
    <p class="govuk-body">
      If character count is different:
    </p>
    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
      <li>Check you pasted the full text (not just part of it)</li>
      <li>Verify you didn't accidentally include extra spaces or line breaks</li>
      <li>Small differences (±5 characters) are fine - formatting may vary slightly</li>
      <li>If significantly different (>10 characters), re-copy and re-paste</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</details>

<div class="govuk-!-margin-top-6">
  <p class="govuk-body">
    Once your chosen announcement text is pasted into Polly, you're ready to generate audio with different voices.
  </p>
</div>

